\f0\fs24 \cf0 The pedagogical motivation\
\pard\pardeftab709\ri0\sl200\ql\qnatural

\fs12 \cf0 The main goal of the development of OAHPA! was to develop a language tutoring system going beyond simple multiple-choice questions or string matching algorithms, with free-form dialogues and sophisticated error analysis. Immediate error feedback and advice about morphology and grammar were seen as important requirements for the program.\
}

